eck 居多<br />\n雖然係會知 但係都有d情況會出到錯<br />\n例如完全同名既人"},{"pid":"56fbfc2e0167777fc326cb6829c4b0bdc7b5e8a7","tid":385244,"uid":36049,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"乜都自己搞咁要班地勤黎把撚😂😂😂<br />\n成班社會廢物。書而讀唔成走去做地勤仲嘈三嘈四"},{"pid":"a93b32c24ec6c5fe1b090c8552a9d1e16812658b","tid":385244,"uid":5637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4同6點根本係自己懶唔想做咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個做哂網上登機你仲洗請你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88da1f6f4b72ccbf39a65a009b9246eb16982729","tid":385244,"uid":89777,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"4同6地勤應該要出手幫先啱喎<br />\n唔係請你嚟做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把人十年都唔出一次國<br />\n實識啦"},{"pid":"de9a085f75667c0be4302a23b28d65e0119a7990","tid":385244,"uid":9315,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"每次笑人地就最快<br />\n比人笑就10萬個藉口<br />\n<br />\n如果篇野笑鳩台灣人就會唔同曬<br />\n睇到我打曬冷震"},{"pid":"6670901d64a0a2a1a88acde9191e38db96590aa5","tid":385244,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/1g0sxn6u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1g0sxn6u&h=bd2e326c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係咁講架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母講咗幾多次咪quote廣告"},{"pid":"32614fce7bffb0ef0cd749819d4ba2cd379ca74f","tid":385244,"uid":61271,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"唔關飛雞地雞事<br />\n<br />\n香港的確好多腦殘阻住個地球轉"},{"pid":"4bb48634c598b5d379bb31c3fefff035bfcecaba","tid":385244,"uid":50740,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意咪辭職囉臭雞"},{"pid":"95e4966a8d501b44c16e3b5ed5b1c6da94d76f2f","tid":385244,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:02:47.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"bb7f5fea5c70e0010b320fbbf939518dfd1fa08b","tid":385244,"uid":2914,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:12:23.000Z","msg":"做得同飛航有關嘅職員都覺得自己特別受氣<br />\n比你地更受氣嘅大有人在<br />\n只不過無人關注<br />\n唔好當自己高人一等<br />\n我番工見過更無理嘅客<br />\n我都無日日上網係到叫苦連天"},{"pid":"b62c1afe572b7b56a0dbce1e715b9f23ff82752f","tid":385244,"uid":5148,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時可以全自動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">炒撚哂班地勤八婆咁閪多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n仲未撚識死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知唔知就係因為仲有佢地鬧果班人（乜都唔識搞）<br />\n佢地先仲有工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果個個識自己搞哂online check in<br />\n第時搞個system自己擺埋行李上輸送帶（自己磅完，scan機票confirm，合標準條輸送帶先郁）<br />\n班地勤應該可以炒一半人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787e68da150d6a527cb617826997e96a286ca4cf","tid":385244,"uid":8423,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"香港人同大陸人一樣<br />\n唔識得自我反省<br />\n比人話就嬲<br />\n但又唔檢討自己係唔係做錯"},{"pid":"7f8cc66a92762e7732b8afad37d9674164b7bec9","tid":385244,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"識d地勤<br />\n又係日鳩日咁fb打文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d840268739d0c33b3a18e12b9fbe38b06a5522","tid":385244,"uid":49634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:45:10.000Z","msg":"乜都唔洗做 炒撚哂你地好唔好<img src=\"/asset